    </section>
    <!-- Application -->
    <section id="application" class="wrapper text-left">
      <div class="lg:grid grid-cols-12">
        <figure class="mb-8 col-start-first col-span-4">
          <img src="/mug.jpg" alt="Leverage branded mug on desk" />
        </figure>
        <div class="col-end-last col-span-7 lg:mt-14">
          <h2 class="text-extrabold mb-4 lg:mb-8">Ready to apply?</h2>
          <div class="content-block">
            <p>We believe the creative agency world is full of multi-talented people. Rather than specific job descriptions, our hope is to learn about anything you're good at, what interests you, or simply what value you think you can bring to a company like Leverage. You may be a developer by trade, but you also happen to love to write â€” that's great, let us know! We'd love for you to reach out and let us know about your talents, what makes you tick, and what you hope to accomplish in your career.</p>
          </div>
          <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" id="form" class="needs-validation mt-14" novalidate style="--primary-color: var(--color-darkgray)">
            <!-- Hidden -->
            <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="c03b3bbe-0911-4575-8186-03c0fa3ec8aa" />
            <input type="checkbox" class="hidden" style="display:none" name="botcheck" />
  
            <ul class="steps mb-10">
              <li class="step h5 active">Step 1</li>
              <li class="step h5">Step 2</li>
              <li class="step h5">Step 3</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="content-block">
              <h4 class="mb-4">First, tell us about your experience.</h4>
              <p>Select as many as you want. Don't see something listed that you're great at? Write it in!</p>
